---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';   // Change this line ONLY if your layout file has a different name

const title = "Brevard County Painting Company | Quality Interior & Exterior";
const description = "Quality house painters serving all of Brevard County, Florida. Clear estimates, proper surface prep, vetted local crews, fair pricing, and Florida-ready materials. Transparent process with full paint records. Get honest advice and a reliable job.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-10">About If Walls Could Talk</h1>

      <!-- SECTION 1 -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">What You Can Expect When You Work With Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">When you hire If Walls Could Talk, you get more than just paint on your walls. You get a properly prepped, long-lasting job with clear communication the entire way.</p>
        <p class="mb-8">Every project includes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li>A clear written estimate before any work starts</li>
          <li>A defined timeline so you always know what's happening</li>
          <li>Regular updates — no radio silence</li>
          <li>Thorough surface preparation</li>
          <li>The right materials for Florida's heat, humidity, and salt air</li>
          <li>Fully insured local crews</li>
          <li>Work performed to written specifications — prep work and materials are never improvised</li>
          <li>A complete paint record at the end — every product used on every surface, so you can match it perfectly years from now</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- SECTION 2 -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Who I Am</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">My name is Heather. I started If Walls Could Talk because I was tired of seeing homeowners disappointed by painting jobs that didn't last — peeling paint after one season, poor prep work, and surprises at the end of the job.</p>
        <p class="mb-6">I built this company through word-of-mouth from real Brevard County homeowners. No ads, no lead generation. Just work that spoke for itself and clients who told other people.</p>
        <p class="mb-6">I started out doing much of the painting work myself. Over time I realized I could help far more Brevard County homeowners by putting the right information in their hands and making sure more local crews were actually following proper standards — not cutting corners to finish faster. That's what this business is built around.</p>
        <p>I genuinely care about protecting your home. Even if you never hire me, I'd rather you leave this site knowing what quality work actually looks like and what questions to ask before letting anyone touch your home.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- SECTION 3 -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">How This Works</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">If Walls Could Talk partners with a small group of vetted, fully insured local crews who follow my detailed written specifications on every project. I review every estimate and set every standard.</p>
        <p>You'll always have me as your single consistent point of contact — making sure you understand your options, what's included, and that you're getting fair value for the work. I'm your personal guide through the whole process.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- SECTION 4 -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Why I Share So Much Free Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">Florida removed its painting license requirement in 2021 — which means literally anyone can show up with a brush and call themselves a professional. Most homeowners don't know that.</p>
        <p>I created the guides, checklists, and articles on this site so you have real tools to protect yourself — whether you hire us or not. An educated homeowner makes the whole process smoother and helps you avoid expensive mistakes down the road.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- SECTION 5 - Contact -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6">Let's Talk About Your Project</h2>
        <p class="mb-8">Whether you have a project in Melbourne, Palm Bay, Titusville, Merritt Island, Cocoa, or anywhere in Brevard County — or you just want honest advice on what to look for when hiring a painter — I'm here.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
          <div class="space-y-4 text-lg">
            <p><strong>Call or text:</strong> <a href="tel:3215576959" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">321-557-6959</a></p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:iwctpaintingplus@gmail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">iwctpaintingplus@gmail.com</a></p>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-600">Or fill out the contact form and I'll get back to you within 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
